Subject: [PATCH 2/3] Fix DLL naming (libzlib.dll -> libz.dll)


diff --git a/CMakeLists.txt b/CMakeLists.txt
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -199,6 +199,11 @@ if(NOT CYGWIN)
